<![CDATA[
Newsletter intro content.

Open the issue clearly and quickly. Help readers understand what this edition covers and why it is worth their attention.
Set up the curated content naturally by previewing the mix of blog posts, links, and discussions included below.
Write in a human, editorial voice that feels welcoming and concise rather than promotional or robotic.
]]>
